 <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎לִבְנֶה‎</span> **noun [masculine]** ==poplar== (apparently = Arabic <img class="bdbSeriacGlyph" src="data:image/gif;base64,">; Ethiopic <img class="bdbSeriacGlyph" src="data:image/gif;base64,"> ***styrax officinalis***; but [[BDB#Sept|ᵐ5]] <span class="bdbLangGreek">λεύκη</span>, compare [[BDB#Syr|ᵑ6]] and [[BDB#Löw|Löw]]<sup>No.107</sup>); — [[Gen.30.37|Gen 30:37]] <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎לַח וְלוּז וְעַרְמוֺן‎</span> <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎׳‎</span><span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎מַקַּל ל‎</span> as marking places of idolatrous incense-burning <span class="bdbLangHebrew">‎תַּחַת אַלּוֺן וְלִבְנֶה וְּאֵלָה‎</span> [[Hos.4.13|Hos 4:13]]. **\*\***named from exuding milky (white) gum De Ges and others.
